            5158,
            10088
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": null
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "Hyundai introduces the loNlQ 5 robotaxi.",
          "block_bbox": [
            0,
            10690,
            3247,
            10868
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "The lONlQ5 is proven worldwide for its prowess in electrification and sustainability.With its global award-winning DNA,Hyundai now begins a pivotal journey with the IONIQ5robotaxi,a level 4 autonomous vehicle that can drive without a driver.More than30 sensors including LiDAR,and a computing system allows the robotaxi to detect360°and make optimal decisions.Hyundai is beginning production ofthe IONIQ5robotaxi,which is set to launch in Las Vegas during the first half of2024.",
          "block_bbox": [
            0,
            10907,
            6255,
            12187
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "HYUNDAI ",
          "block_bbox": [
            8099,
            12549,
            9838,
            12830
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "footer",
          "block_content": "Computer generated images shown,and actual production model may vary.The vehicle is not available for purchase.\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            0,
            12788,
            4357,
            13102
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": null
        }
      ],
      "markdown": "# Excellence goes autonomous.\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_2622_2328_10000_6571.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"73%\" /></div>\n\n\nIONIQ5robotaxi \n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_18_6537_5158_10088.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"51%\" /></div>\n\n\n## Hyundai introduces the loNlQ 5 robotaxi\n\nThe lONlQ5 is proven worldwide for its prowess in electrification and sustainability.With its global award-winning DNA,Hyundai now begins a pivotal journey with the IONIQ5robotaxi,a level 4 autonomous vehicle that can drive without a driver.More than30 sensors including LiDAR,and a computing system allows the robotaxi to detect360°and make optimal decisions.Hyundai is beginning production ofthe IONIQ5robotaxi,which is set to launch in Las Vegas during the first half of2024.\n\n## HYUNDAI ",
